#'''''eudicot''''' any plant belonging to the group labelled "eudicots" in modern plant systematics. Eudicots have the features known as typical for [[dicotyledon]]s. Eudicots are [[birch]]es, [[rose]]s, [[sunflower]]s, etc, but not [[magnolia]]s, waterlilies, etc.
